data.description: Welcome to your new home nestled within the tranquil confines of a picturesque cul-de-sac. This charming property boasts a plethora of recent updates, ensuring both aesthetic appeal and functional excellence. Upgrades include a new fence, working sprinkler system, upgraded baseboards and kitchen counter tops and much much more! Schedule your private tour today and come see for yourself.
